## 1. Deep Smart Contract Audit & Additional Schema Additions

During the comprehensive audit of all smart contracts under `CRATS-EVM/contracts` (Layers 1 – 4), we identified and added **8 missing specialized models** to ensure 100% coverage across all RWA asset types, off-chain document registries, yield dividends, physical redemptions, and cross-border compliance:

### 1. Asset Category Plugins (`contracts/asset/plugins/`)
- **`RealEstateMetadata`**: Property identity, square footage, appraisal value USD, zoning class, location address, occupancy rate.
- **`FineArtMetadata`**: Artwork title, artist name, medium, creation year, appraisal value USD, provenance IPFS URI, authentication certificate SHA-256 hash.

### 2. Off-Chain Document Registry (DMS v4) (`contracts/asset/DMSRegistry.sol`)
- **`DmsDocument`**: Document ID, Asset ID, Document Type (`PROSPECTUS`, `APPRAISAL`, `PDD`, `VERIFICATION`, `TITLE_DEED`), Content SHA-256 Hash, File URI, Expiry Date, Verification Status.

### 3. Financial Yield & Physical Redemptions (`contracts/financial/`)
- **`YieldDistribution`**: Dividend distribution ID, Vault address, Total yield USD, Yield per share, Snapshot block number, TxHash, Timestamp.
- **`YieldClaim`**: Claim ID, Distribution ID, Investor address, Yield amount claimed, TxHash.
- **`PhysicalRedemption`**: Physical RWA redemption ID, Token address, Investor address, Token amount burned/escrowed, Physical status (`REQUESTED`, `APPROVED`, `SHIPPED`, `SETTLED`, `REJECTED`), Delivery tracking reference.

### 4. Cross-Border VASP Compliance & Investor Governance (`contracts/compliance/`, `contracts/identity/`)
- **`TravelRuleVaspLog`**: Originator address (`@sender`), Beneficiary address (`@receiver`), Originator VASP ID, Beneficiary VASP ID, USD Amount, Compliance status (`PASSED`, `BLOCKED`, `FLAGGED`).
- **`InvestorRightsLog`**: Token address, Investor address, Voting power, Dividend entitlement %, Inspection rights status.

